    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Die veneris qui fuit septimus exeuntis mensis ianuarii, <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum virorum</rs> presentia quorum
                        nomina inferius scripta invenientur. <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Ordinatio #Forests #Mansi #marriage"
                            ref="#people/3571">Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio et dux</rs>
                        <rs key="#Ordinatio">investivit</rs> dompnum <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries #Missus #Ordinatio" ref="#people/3568"
                            >Haeinricum</persName>, <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Monks #Missus #Ordinatio #Forests #Mansi"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName> quod est
                        haedificatum in <rs key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches">episcopatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches" ref="#places/275"
                            >Mantuano</placeName> iuxta <rs key="#Rivers">flumen</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/4196">Padi Vetuli</placeName>, per
                        dompnum <persName key="#Monks #Missus #Ordinatio" ref="#people/4001"
                            >Girbertum</persName> et dompnurn <persName
                            key="#Monks #Missus #Ordinatio" ref="#people/4002">Ogerium</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">nuncios</rs> ipsius
                        dompni Haeinrici abbatis, vice totius congregationis ipsius monasterii,
                        scilicet de <rs key="#Mansi">mansis</rs> tribus et dimidio terre cum <rs
                            key="#Forests">busco</rs> positis in <geogName
                            key="#Forests #Mansi #Ordinatio" ref="#estates/2094">silva de <placeName
                                key="#Forests" ref="#places/34">Piguniaga</placeName></geogName>,
                        loco <placeName key="#Mansi #Forests #Ordinatio" ref="#places/4194"
                            >Castiniolo</placeName>, infra coherentias inferius hic nominatas, id
                        est: a mane iuris ipsius monasterii, a meridie similiter iuris ipsius
                        rnonasterii et idem Albertus marchio et dux, a sera similiter idem Albertus
                        marchio et dux, a septemtrione predictum flumen Padi Vetuli. Et insuper
                        investivit de tota terra que noviter runcata erat iuxta ipsam silvam
                        Castiniolo et iuxta silvam que dicitur <placeName key="#Forests #Ordinatio"
                            ref="#places/4192">Carpeneda</placeName>, et est terra illa <rs
                            key="#Size">iugera novem, tabulas quadraginta minus</rs>. Tali modo ipse
                        Albertus marchio et dux investivit ipsum dompnum abbatem per iamdictos
                        nuncios suos vice totius congregationis, ut liceat ei eiusque fratribus
                        eorumque successoribus ipsos mansos runcare et terram ipsam et predicta
                        iugera novem, tabulas quadraginta minus, in perpetuum colere et gaudere et
                        habere, et quicquid voluerint facere ad eorum usum et utilitatem sine omni
                        ipsius Alberti marchionis et ducis suorumque haeredum contraditione. Et
                        insuper promisit ipse marchio et dux ipse et eius haeredes totam predictam
                        terram iamdicto monasterio omni tempore ab omni homine defendere; quod si
                        defendere non potuerit, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eam terram
                        ipso monasterio componere debet. Actum est hoc in loco <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/2967">Bondino</placeName>, in camera ipsius
                        marchionis, iuxta <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Iacobi</orgName>, adstante ibi <rs
                            key="#marriage">uxore</rs> eius. Anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo vigesimo nono, predicto die, inditione septima. Interfuerunt ibi:
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness #parentOf"><name
                                ref="Maleadobatus/de Cuvriago">Maleadobatus</name></persName> de
                            <placeName>Curviago</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness #childOf"><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> eius, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name ref="Malabranca"
                                >Malabranca</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness childOf"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Girardus</name></persName> filius <persName
                            key="#parentOf #childOf"><name ref="Gherardus">Girardi</name></persName>
                        filii <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"><name
                                ref="Heinricus/de Bondino">Inricus</name></persName> de Bondino, et
                        rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (SN) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Ordinatio"><name ref="Bonus"
                            >Bonus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii his interfui, rogatus <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
